det är ju mkv-fil det går ju inte å bränna hur gör man om den??

1. Download Avidemux
2. Open the MKV file for CD1
3. Append CD2's MKV
4. Save as AVI, keep both video and audio at "Copy" mode
5. It should work in a proper stand-alone DivX DVD player
